00:56:49.960 --> 00:56:54.980
It's designed to be extremely easy to work with, like abstract away all the painful stuff.

00:56:54.980 --> 00:56:57.960
And it's also designed to be really easy to contribute to.

00:56:57.960 --> 00:57:03.080
